# Operator

**Skills/roles**

 - start and run a one person for profit LLC
 - create, edit, replicate a magic book
 - create and maintain a raspberry pi server with all the elements of geometron
 - buy a domain, pay for hosting, maintain a public facing web page
 - build and replicate physical media pointing to the domain
 - "sell" the network to business owners as promoter
 - use grant template to raise STEM education grant money
 - work events, do gigs as teacher
 - work with public library to funnel technology resources into public spaces
 - mutual aid work
 - promote our own side hustles and those of people around us
 - teach another operator to run the entire system


